and the ??? for it is pretty close to the telepoint. So I cleared the spiders there so they wouldnt link, and for TP.  I then take a knee to med some mp back, and tell my buddy im going to hit the bathroom and be right back. <br>  <br> I get back and have a seat. I start to type &quot;Ok, once my mp is full i'll buff up (blink, protect, regen, eat a bob) and then...&quot; <br>  <br> By the time I get to that spot in the sentence, suddenly two spiders pop. My first and second thoughts when this happened: <br>  <br> &quot;Hey, two desert spiders popped at the same time, I'll guess I'll have to clear them&quot; <br>  <br> &quot;Uhhh...oh...ummm...&quot; <br>  <br> Sure enough, he popped the two NMs by accident. Eek. <br>  <br> Time to spring into action. (Note: because of the suddeness of the pops, I had no time to buff and wasnt thinking clearly) He had utsusemi up so the spiders were munching on the shadows when I jumped up and stunned one, when that spider came up to me I opened with Guillotine, the spider was whacking away so I cast drain on the other spider to get it off the Nin. While this is happening, I notice the nins health is still dropping so I figure I dont have enough hate. So I cast poisonga and stun on the other spider. I had hate the whole time though, the health was dropping was because the spider had poisoned the ninja and it eats away like 30hp a tick. I try to target the nin and Cure3 him, but he drops dead. Uh oh. <br>  <br> Both spiders are still up. After a little bit I hit my first cure3, which slows the damage for a bit. My health then drops to about 60 percent so I Souleater/Bloodweaponed. Bloodweapon runs out, so I cancel souleater. The first spider drops, one left. However, I wasted about 150mp already at this point on the two stuns, poisonga, cure3 and drain. Im not at full health and have lost more than half of my mp already, and this other spider is still looking at me. <br>  <br> Well, I had enough tp a little bit into the fight with the scond spider to guillotine, this drops it to about 5/8 health, with me probably being at 6/8. I hit cure 3 which cripples the MP front. Now the weird part. A random blm who was walking around and somehow found himself in the little knob where the fight takes place. I ask him to raise my friend while im fighting and he does, so if I do win he can click the ??? and get his item. Then before I can say &quot;hey, can you spare a cure?&quot; the blm is gone. Oh well. <br>  <br> I had only enough mp left for one drain, so I hit it. Resist. I get 60 hp back. Shouldve cure2'd. Alas. <br>  <br> Fight isnt looking good as the spider hits for 50-75 damage and I have no mp left. I get down to about 400hp, when suddenly I have enough tp for guillotine. Dead spider. And there was much rejoicing &lt;yay...&gt; <br>  <br> End of the fight stats - HP 378/1199 MP 6/249. Goo. <br>  <br> Was very lucky. My guillotines were each for at least 800 damage, which means all four hits landed. The spiders never sickle slashed, one would have made it interesting, two would have been death. They used their tp attacks for acid spray and spider web, both of which missed. Had I been poisoned it probably wouldve been curtains too. I also didnt miss once the whole fight. Just a lot of luck. But my buddy got his AF and I get to feel warm and fuzzy. <br>  <br> How I wish I would have thought to have Sleep 2'd a spider to start the fight...but like I said, wasnt expecting the pop, wasnt thinking straight. <br>  <br> Sorry for the long story. But it was fun. <img src="http://media.ign.com/boardfaces/1.gif" border="0" alt="happy" hspace="0" vspace="0">  <br> <p></p><span class="SignatureTitle">-----signature-----</span><div class="SignatureText">Mertron (I'd rather be fishing - level 42) <br> Rank 8 San d'Oria, Fairy <br> 63DRK, 37WAR, 37THF, 29RDM, 18MNK, 16NIN, 14WHM, 7 BST, 5BLM <br> You've only got one shot. And it will take more than that to stop me. <br>  <br> </div><